## Toggling On/Off

**To enable:**
1. Set `auto_apply: true` in this file
2. Restart Claude Code

**To disable:**
1. Set `auto_apply: false` in this file
2. Restart Claude Code

**Or delete the file entirely** to disable automatic repetition.

