## Troubleshooting

**Repetition not applying:**
- Check that this file is named `.claude/prompt-repeater.local.md` (not `.example`)
- Verify `auto_apply: true` is set
- Restart Claude Code (hooks load at session start)

**Want different modes for different tasks:**
- Keep `auto_apply: false`
- Use `/repeat-last`, `/repeat-verbose`, or `/repeat-3x` commands selectively

**Repetition applying when you don't want it:**
- Set `auto_apply: false` and restart Claude Code
- Or delete this file entirely
